\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

The FOC w.r.t X and A are
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray}
p_{x} & = & \pi_{z}g=MC(X)\nonumber \\
\frac{dp_{x}}{dA} & = & \pi_{z}Xg'=p_{a}\label{eq:5}
\end{eqnarray}

\end_inset

By (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
